Never so much.

4
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:13,780
Whatever was said, this was not good they would do.

5
00:00:13,780 --> 00:00:15,860
Knowingly that they are doing wrong.

6
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:19,920
If they were good people they would say, all right, this is good, we'll do the good.

7
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:23,460
But everybody knew that this was wrong or right.

8
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:26,100
They may do it.

9
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:30,780
And today no one knows what is wrong and what is right.

10
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:36,220
Apart from wrong and right, it's much beyond that you have to know yourself.

11
00:00:36,220 --> 00:00:40,220
Because this awareness is within us that we do not know ourselves.

12
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:41,740
We do not know the absolute.

13
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:43,620
We live in a relative world.

14
00:00:43,620 --> 00:00:50,980
