15
00:00:50,980 --> 00:00:57,460
But definitely there's a feeling in every one of us that we do not know.

16
00:00:57,460 --> 00:01:04,180
And it's a very honest feeling, it's a very sublime feeling that we have to know something

17
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:05,180
more.

18
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:11,940
Now when we say the word no, we think, as if I would say, I don't know about the Bishar,

19
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,780
I've never been there.

20
00:01:13,780 --> 00:01:15,140
Now this means what?

21
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:17,420
I don't know about the Bishar.

22
