00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:31,500
I would not know till I meet somebody who is really belonging to that place who knows

42
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:33,780
about it.

43
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:40,340
In the same way the knowledge that we have also about Divine is very confusing.

44
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:44,540
But this is not knowledge, this is never the knowledge.

45
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:55,460
The idea of knowledge comes to us as if it is a kind of an answer to our inquiries which

46
00:02:55,460 --> 00:03:00,940
is rational, which we can understand intelligently through our intelligence.

47
00:03:00,940 --> 00:03:06,500
But now this area is beyond intelligence, beyond rationality.

48
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:12,260
Beyond all that is limited, it's the unlimited area.

49
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:20,100
Such unlimited areas can be only known by experience of your awareness.

50
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:26,460
Now this one should understand is a very delicate thing, how to know something and experience

