61
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:06,860
He sees it.

62
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:15,020
Awareness, the human awareness has so many great things about itself compared to the animal

63
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:17,620
awareness.

64
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:26,460
For example we can say the awareness of beauty, animal's don't have, awareness of cleanliness,

65
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:28,740
animals don't have.

66
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:34,340
Human beings have these built within themselves.

67
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:35,900
They can feel it.

68
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:40,300
They can feel it on the central nervous system.

69
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:45,300
So whatever is your awareness is to be felt on your central nervous system.

70
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:49,660
It's not just an imaginary thing or an intellectual discussion.

71
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:52,700
I say, yes I know, I don't, not that.

72
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:57,140
The knowledge should come to you through your feelings.

73
00:04:57,140 --> 00:05:04,900
