74
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:09,780
In the same way the feeling has to come through your central nervous system.

75
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:14,940
That means your awareness itself is to be going, it has to be charged.

76
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:17,140
It has to get a new dimension.

77
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:20,860
Your awareness itself has to get a new dimension.

78
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:26,460
All other experiences has no meaning whatsoever in evolution if you see.

79
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:33,420
In evolutionary process it is the awareness that improves, receives better and better

80
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,980
dimensions.

81
